messages.content: Annual Revenue Target: $15 Million. The company aims to achieve this with a 76% year-over-year growth from the previous year's annual revenue of $8.5 Million.
who is your ceo and what is the background of CEO?
Sarah Johnson is the Chief Executive Officer (CEO) of the company. She has a background as a former VP of Engineering at Google Cloud, with an MBA from Stanford GSB and BS Computer Science from MIT.
